rows.label: qev031503_MSG0001
rows.name:
Ha ha! Many beasts approach!
More than most see in lifetime![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031503_MSG0002
rows.name: Such entertainment! Are you ready, Earth alien?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031503_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell Slovity that you are ready anytime.

rows.label: qev031503_SEL0021
rows.name: Say that you need more time.

rows.label: qev031503_MSG0003
rows.name: Said and done. Now let us begin![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031503_MSG0004
rows.name: ...And you! Oche Wolfen! Do you come too?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031503_MSG0005
rows.name: Of course. I will show you bravery of Tree Clan![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031503_MSG0006
rows.name: We will see. Now let us crush disaster underfoot![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031503_MSG0007
rows.name: Hurry then! I have waited too long for good fight.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031503_MSG0008
rows.name:
I pushed myself to limit in training.
Then used that skill here. Nothing beats giant brawl![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031503_MSG0009
rows.name:
Ganglion, Prone, or beast, I do not care.
I want to rampage more![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031503_MSG0010
rows.name:
...Idiots. Who cares about Tree Clan or Cavern Clan?
This is no time for Prone to fight each other![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031503_MSG0011
rows.name:
But so be it. If they refuse my aid,
I fight on my own terms.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031503_MSG0012
rows.name: You help them. Weaklings need you more than I.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031503_MSG0013
rows.name: Beasts are nearly here. Must we face new enemy?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031503_MSG0014
rows.name:
Consider them warm-up, Earth alien.
That much should be simple for you! Ha ha ha![ST:wait ]
